The paper deals with privacy-preserving data publishing, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a language to express background knowledge about the data, which is a concept that is commonly used in databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses algorithms and methods for measuring and sanitizing data, which are topics that fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the disclosure of sensitive information, which is a topic that falls under information theory (cs.IT).
